{% comment -%}
This component just includes the regular last six steps of a site change on a docs page.

It makes the doc md file easier to read and edit.  The 6 steps are other files in this folder.

Run pa11y on the pages you changed.

Run html proofer on the site.

Run pa11y-ci on the site.

Commit all your changes to GitHub.

Request approval of your changes from the original requestor.

Merge with the main branch.
{% endcomment -%}
